net.objectof.impl.corc.requests

Class IRequestor<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.objectof.impl.corc.IHandler<T>
      • net.objectof.impl.corc.requests.IRequestor<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Handler<T>, Interface<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IService, IStreamAdaptor, IWebHandler, IWebHandler

    public abstract class IRequestor<T>
extends IHandler<T>
    An abstract class to manage a transaction. Concrete classes:
    • override onExecute() to send() sub-requests on based on this transaction.
    • override getStatus() to determine when the transaction is completed.
    Author:
    jdh
